{"tid":1501934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中 改名做 “反送共”","createTime":"2019-08-24T13:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:21:02.000Z","uid":74090,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8f23dc3e9efb026ae63e093222de34ff5b526119","tid":1501934,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"一直以黎全香港都用反送中做標語口號<br />\n今日台灣有學者對呢個口號俾左啲建議<br />\n提議反送中應改名做 &ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">反送共</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n認為應該係反對送去共產政權<br />\n要針對共產政權，而唔係針對中國<br />\n個人認為甚有道理，各位覺得點？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DEq7raIl5to\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDEq7raIl5to&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOtTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=ac2df6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DEq7raIl5to</a>  可由第48分鐘睇起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKWmMPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKWmMPg.png&h=75d1ddb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBVOrPm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBVOrPm.png&h=c5b760de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4JHwgo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4JHwgo.png&h=0b000eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Orqe6PP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrqe6PP.png&h=39538120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZ0ZyuW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZ0ZyuW.png&h=74c4403e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30OrP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30OrP1.png&h=0181d6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGN5t3t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGN5t3t.png&h=3dc7ee28&s={SIZE}\"